T* (be due for properly performed work if the consumer withdraws after VANTAM has begun work) Tj
T* (at the consumer's request.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Possible loss of the withdrawal right after complete performance applies only where all) Tj
T* (statutory conditions are met, including the required prior request, acknowledgement, and) Tj
T* (durable-medium confirmation.) Tj
T* () Tj
