T* (or another lawful agreed amount stated in the accepted Offer.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (After work begins, VANTAM may charge only pre-agreed work actually performed and) Tj
T* (pre-approved third-party costs. Any required refund must be made according to applicable) Tj
T* (law and the accepted written agreement.) Tj
T* () Tj
